# WikiQuiz AI - Wikipedia to Quiz Generator ğŸ§ âœ¨

A full-stack AI application that transforms any Wikipedia article into an interactive quiz in seconds. It uses **Google Gemini Pro** to generate questions, **FastAPI** for the backend, and **React** for a responsive frontend.

